            explanation:
              "Calculate: log10(86.36 - 40.64) = log10(45.72) Γëê 1.660, log10(177.8) Γëê 2.250",
          },
          {
            label: "Step 4",
            explanation:
              "Body Fat % = 86.010 ├ù 1.660 - 70.041 ├ù 2.250 + 36.76 Γëê 142.77 - 157.59 + 36.76 = 21.94%",
