        <p className="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Maintaining an ideal weight is crucial for a dogΓÇÖs overall health, longevity, and quality of life. This calculator helps pet owners estimate the optimal daily calorie intake required to maintain their dogΓÇÖs ideal weight, taking into account the dogΓÇÖs current condition and activity level. Unlike human BMI formulas, veterinary science uses metabolic scaling laws to accurately estimate energy needs based on body weight raised to the 0.75 power, reflecting the unique physiology of dogs.
