          How to Use This Calculator
        </h2>
        <p className="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          To accurately assess your horseΓÇÖs risk of toxic plant poisoning, provide the following information in the calculator. Enter your horseΓÇÖs weight using the selected unit system, estimate the amount of the toxic plant ingested, select the specific plant type, and input the time elapsed since ingestion. This data allows the tool to calculate a risk ratio based on veterinary toxicology standards.
        </p>
        <ul className="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <li>
            <strong>Step 1:</strong> Enter your horseΓÇÖs weight in pounds or kilograms depending on the unit system selected.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Step 2:</strong> Estimate the amount of the toxic plant ingested, either in pounds or grams.
          </li>
