            <strong>Step 3:</strong> Select the toxic plant type from the dropdown menu (e.g., Ragwort, Yew, Oleander).
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Step 4:</strong> Enter the time since ingestion in hours to help contextualize the risk.
          </li>
