        </p>
        <ul className="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <li>
            <strong>Step 1:</strong> Weigh your reptile using a precise scale to ensure dosing accuracy.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Step 2:</strong> Select the unit system matching your weight measurement.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Step 3:</strong> Choose the appropriate drug from the list based on veterinary guidance.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Step 4:</strong> Click ΓÇ£CalculateΓÇ¥ to obtain the dose in milligrams, and follow your veterinarianΓÇÖs instructions for administration frequency and duration.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Step 5:</strong> Use the ΓÇ£ResetΓÇ¥ button to clear inputs and perform new calculations as needed.
          </li>
        </ul>
